Laba ka mid ah maraakiibta nooca Trump ayaa la dhisi doonaa bilowga laakiin tiradaas ayaa laga yaabaa inay si weyn u koraan mustaqbalka, sida laga soo xigtay madaxweynaha, oo sheegay inay noqon doonaan "qaar ka mid ah maraakiibta dagaalka ee ugu halista badan" iyo "markabkii ugu weynaa ee taariikhda dalkeena." Trump ayaa hadalkan ka sheegay hoygiisa Mar-a-Lago ee Florida oo ay weheliyaan madaxa Pentagon Pete Hegseth, xoghayaha arrimaha dibadda Marco Rubio iyo xoghayaha ciidamada badda John Phelan, iyadoo sawirada maraakiibta casriga ah ee la qorsheeyay ay taagan yihiin meel u dhow.
